Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:06.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Matsuhashi Miki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hint to reasoning is to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a mystery behind every case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two revolutions in a day, a unique house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A surprising trick and surprising solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeking the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the appearance of a child\Nand the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.74,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Something's just not right
